article.headline: Gillespie has 14 points including the game-winning free throw to get Belmont past Lipscomb 72-71

images.name: Lipscomb Bisons vs. Belmont Bruins: Full Highlights
images.caption: Lipscomb Bisons vs. Belmont Bruins: Full Highlights

article.linkText: Gillespie has 14 points including the game-winning free throw to get Belmont past Lipscomb 72-71
article.story: NASHVILLE, Tenn. -- — Malik Dia scored 15 points and Ja'Kobi Gillespie secured the victory with a free throw with five seconds remaining as Belmont took down Lipscomb 72-71 on Wednesday night. Dia was 5-of-9 shooting and 3 of 4 from the free-throw line for the Bruins (7-3). Cade Tyson scored 14 points and added five rebounds. Gillespie had 14 points and shot 6 for 11, including 1 for 5 from beyond the arc. Will Pruitt led the way for the Bisons (6-5) with 21 points, nine rebounds and four assists. Derrin Boyd added 12 points for Lipscomb. Cody Head also put up nine points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
